Uber driver Emerson Decarvalho allegedly ran down a cyclist after ramming into a cyclist who was shouting at him , leaving the biker with several broken bones , police say .
The incident occurred in the busy Fisherman 's Wharf area of San Francisco when the cyclist rode up to the vehicle , banged on his window .
The driver , Emerson Emerson , 38 , stayed at the scene of the crash and was charged with assault with a deadly weapon after the incident .